There are flagged files in Conference (<conf num>) <conf name>
Do you want to leave without downloading them?(y/n/s/A/g/?)>:

(y)es, forget them.
(n)o, Back to the BBS!
(s)ave them till next call.
(A)ll save. Save all flags and quit now!
(g)oodbye, now!

